	<li style="font-family: Arial">ACCEPTABLE FOODS: dry beans and
lentils, rice and grains, pasta, oats, flour
(especially unique ones like cassava flour!),
coffee and tea, cooking oil and olive oil,
sugar, salt, reusable shopping bags, rolling
carts (for carrying food)</li>
	<li style="font-family: Arial">NOT ACCEPTED: glass containers, canned
foods, perishable foods, or items that weigh
over 5lb each.</li>
</ul>
<p><i>Information</i>, 
