Leavenworth. This year, Jesuit and Ignatian-inspired
partners team up at this special place along the
Wenatchee River. No need to be an artist—just bring
your creative self! Faculty: Ceramics for the Table,
Arturo Aurajo, SJ; From Shrine to the Divine: Making
Home Altars, Fernando Alvarez-Lara, SJ; Printmaking,
